page.title: 01Area South East of Colkirk
page.content: Area is basically slightly rolling farm land with a few woods mainly deciduous, and seeral spinnies mainly conifers recently planted. There are eight farms:- Colkirk Hull Farm, dairy and some arable; Testerton Hull farm, arable; Westwood farm, arable; Hazelwood farm, Piggeries; Killma farm, poultry; Selby Fruit farm, orchards; Hamrow farm, Orchards and arable. Square 1 consits of part of the village of Colkirk which is mainly a dormatory for the surounding area and retired people.
